text: Bounlap Khenkitisack (born June 18, 1966) is a Laotian professional footballer and football manager. He played for Yotha F.C..YOTHA FC: BOUNLAP KHENKITISACK THE LEGEND OF YOTHA FC!!! From October 2004, to 2005,Laos pledges to beat S’pore, revive Vietnam’s hope — Vietnam Breaking News and from January to February 2011 he coached the Laos national football team. ==Manager== Lao Toyota * Lao Premier League 16px Champions (1); 2017 ==References== ==External links== *Profile at Soccerway.com *Profile at Soccerpunter.com Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Laotian footballers Category:Yotha F.C. players Category:Laotian football managers Category:Laos national football team managers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
